      "event_id": "70904110_e00020",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "管和"
      ],
      "text": "管和。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00021",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田昆"
      ],
      "text": "众位将军请了。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00022",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "田常",
        "田玉",
        "田能",
        "管和",
        "廉赛花"
      ],
      "text": "请了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00023",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田昆"
      ],
      "text": "国母登台点将，你我两相伺候。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00024",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四女兵、大刀手引钟无盐同上。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00025",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "端正好",
      "speakers": [
        "钟无盐"
      ],
      "text": "没来由，风波起，急忙忙催趲征驹。都只为保定了俺东齐，楚王他暗设杀机，俺必须紧紧防提。",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00026",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "田常",
        "田玉",
        "田能",
        "管和",
        "田昆",
        "廉赛花"
      ],
      "text": "参见国母。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00027",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟无盐"
      ],
      "text": "众位将军少礼。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00028",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "钟无盐"
      ],
      "text": "宝剑霜威耀苍穹，霓旌慢卷午西风。一声呼啸貔貅肃，龙驹飞腾天下惊。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00029",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟无盐"
      ],
      "text": "哀家钟离春，别号无盐，扶保齐王，且喜言听计从，方得国泰民安，四海实服，人人敬仰。众将官。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00030",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "田常",
        "田玉",
        "田能",
        "管和",
        "田昆",
        "廉赛花"
      ],
      "text": "国母。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00031",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟无盐"
      ],
      "text": "可恨楚邦，暗生诡计，养一个猴头，封为丞相，自负弈棋，无敌于天下，他今邀请吾主与哀家前去赴棋盘大会，我想此乃三分请会七分战，只恐到时必有一场风波颠险。位此今日登台点将，以防不测。",
      "text_length": 88
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00032",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "田常",
        "田玉",
        "田能",
        "管和",
        "田昆",
        "廉赛花"
      ],
      "text": "国母。有用臣等之处，理当尽心尽力，以报我主之恩。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00033",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟无盐"
      ],
      "text": "好，听我道来。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00034",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "叨叨令",
      "speakers": [
        "钟无盐"
      ],
      "text": "哪怕他重重的罗网奇，俺今番可也难回避。他那里分明是擒凤牢笼计，说什么意重心诚兄弟谊。兀的不恨煞人也么哥，兀的不恼煞人也么哥，告诸臣须记取棋盘会不是待客的筵席。",
      "text_length": 79
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00035",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "齐王"
      ],
      "text": "圣驾到。https://scripts.xikao.com/play/709041102022-01-27",
      "text_length": 53
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00036",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "田常",
        "田玉",
        "田能",
        "管和",
        "田昆",
        "廉赛花"
      ],
      "text": "驾到。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00037",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟无盐"
      ],
      "text": "啊，是我背了大王点齐众将，以防不测，不想大王驾到，随我接驾。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00038",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四小太监、二大太监引齐王同上。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00039",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟无盐"
      ],
      "text": "参见大王！千千岁。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00040",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "齐王"
      ],
      "text": "平身。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00041",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟无盐"
      ],
      "text": "千千岁。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00042",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "齐王"
      ],
      "text": "梓童，众将为何披挂整齐，聚至教场？",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00043",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟无盐"
      ],
      "text": "这，妾身要登台点将，调遣人马，预做埋伏，以防万一。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00044",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "齐王"
      ],
      "text": "梓童差矣。想我齐邦威镇列国，诸侯丧胆，楚邦与我力求和好，此番江楼会棋，乃是衣冠之会，如此大兴人马，岂不有碍邦交？",
      "text_length": 56
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00045",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟无盐"
      ],
      "text": "大王，想列国争强，各怀心机，外托宴乐之名，内藏甲兵，前车之鉴，大王不可不妨。",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00046",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "齐王"
      ],
      "text": "如此，梓童小做安排就是。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00047",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟无盐"
      ],
      "text": "是。吩咐击鼓登台。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00048",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田常"
      ],
      "text": "击鼓登台。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00049",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟无盐"
      ],
      "text": "田常、田玉听令。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00050",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "田常",
        "田玉"
      ],
      "text": "在。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00051",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟无盐"
      ],
      "text": "命你二人改扮马童模样，随哀家前去赴会。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00052",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "田常",
        "田玉"
      ],
      "text": "得令。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00053",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "田常、田玉同下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00054",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟无盐"
      ],
      "text": "田能、管和听令。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00055",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "田能",
        "管和"
      ],
      "text": "在。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00056",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟无盐"
      ],
      "text": "命你等带领人马，埋伏在丹凤岭。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00057",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "田能",
        "管和"
      ],
      "text": "得令。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00058",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟无盐"
      ],
      "text": "田昆听令。命你带领三千人马在盘龙山接应，不得有误。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00059",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田昆"
      ],
      "text": "得令。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00060",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "齐王"
      ],
      "text": "啊梓童，盘龙山既有埋伏，又何必如此兴师动众，此事倘被列国闻之，不笑我齐邦忒胆小了。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00061",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟无盐"
      ],
      "text": "大王，岂不知既防其一，必防其二，有备无患，方为万全。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00062",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "齐王"
      ],
      "text": "就依梓童，急速启程，荆楚一游。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70904110_e00063",
      "play_id": "70904110",
      "scene_id": "70904110_s01",
